Provogue Slippers Price: Rs.1188

Provogue introduces this trendy pair of slippers that can keep your soles happy and comfortable with their cushioned footbeds. These slippers can be a part of your closet for years to come as they are made of leather.

Slippers from the celebrated fashion house of Provogue epitomise the modern man – elegant
